casebody.data:
Frank Compolattaro, Jr. v. Richard Compolattaro et al. (9613)

O’Connell, Lavery and Ripley, Js.

Argued September 25 decision released October 15, 1991 Rhonna W. Rogol, with whom, on the brief, was Robert M. Wechsler, for the appellants (defendants). John Wayne Fox, with whom, on the brief, was Susan L. Stratton, for the appellee (plaintiff). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
